data.name: lb_unstick.ToolTip
data.value: Depending on the map your character may get stuck on a ladder or rope. Although the macro does auto fix eventually to optimise farming rates we can manually jump off at a more frequent rate. NOTE: You may get better rates on certain maps without this feature on

data.name: lb_information.Text
data.value:
Ensure 'Num Lock' is disabled, RuneSolver is running as admin and Maplestory client is in focus for auto rune to work correctly.
It may take up to 5 minutes to deactivate session if you close without manually logging out
